{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_slbell_set_1", "eventName": "雪山外", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "雪山外", "storyInfo": "喀蘭聖女在各方之間周旋，只為了有片刻可以卸下聖女的重擔，以初雪的身份短暫休憩。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g3_mainhall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$distressed_intro", "key": "$distressed_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 耶拉岡德在上。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 耶拉岡德在上。", "name": "眾長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 實在抱歉，為了經學以外的事情而麻煩各位長老前來大殿。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 這次卡西米爾商業代表提出求見喀蘭的聖女，各位長老是怎麼想的呢？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 荒唐可笑的想法，外人豈能隨便見到聖女大人？", "name": "嚴肅的長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 況且，聖山也容不得外人踏足。", "name": "嚴肅的長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 確實，如果將世俗事務都請進蔓珠院來，恐怕會過於打擾各位的清淨。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 但作為謝拉格的管理者，我如果回絕對方的邀請，則難免會在外交層面造成不良影響。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 與外人談生意，從來都是恩希歐迪斯的事。卡西米爾來的不過是一介商人，他想與聖女大人攀談，本來就是僭越。", "name": "嚴肅的長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 恐怕不能這麼說。在卡西米爾，商業聯合會的權勢不容小覷。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#10$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 而且，正因為卡西米爾有發達的商業和龐大的資本，我很擔憂他們會以此施壓，給謝拉格帶來一份不利的合約。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 商業聯合會派遣代表來謝拉格，預示著他們有多方面合作的意願。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 更重要的是，他們直接求見了聖女，這其中的意圖顯然已經超過了商業範疇。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 一份與喀蘭貿易的合約只是開端。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 而恩希歐迪斯，他畢竟只是希瓦艾什家族的領袖，他所能做出的許諾和擔保，無法比我更有分量。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 聖女大人如果親自見外來人......這一行為本身就足夠有分量。", "name": "慈祥的長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我正是這樣想的。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 所以聖女大人這是決意要將外人帶到蔓珠院來？", "name": "嚴肅的長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不，聖山畢竟是聖山，蔓珠院也是謝拉格的聖地，我不願令耶拉岡德不悅。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 因此，我會下山去接見卡西米爾的代表。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 這......", "name": "嚴肅的長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 僅為外人一個冒犯的請求就下山，實在是有失體統。", "name": "嚴肅的長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 謝拉格的子民每日虔誠祈禱，都難得見到聖女大人一面，他一個外來人，怎麼能隨隨便便就見到聖女？", "name": "嚴肅的長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 嗯，我也希望對方能感受到這次會面十分難得，所以信眾來拜耶拉岡德時的一系列禮儀，我會要求他照做。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 至於謝拉格的民眾......也許這一次他們還不會知道聖女的動向，不過以後，他們終歸會接受這種轉變。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#10$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 隨著謝拉格與外界的聯繫日益緊密，想必會有更多政治人士前來謝拉格尋求會面，我也必須承擔起對應的責任。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#10$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 另外，也請各位長老權衡。放任恩希歐迪斯做他的生意，各位應該清楚會有什麼後果。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 為了換來工業技術，喀蘭貿易對外簽訂了許多對我們並不有利的合約，這是實情。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我並不是要質疑恩希歐迪斯，他這樣也是無奈之舉。但我希望這種形勢能逐漸向對謝拉格更加有利的方向轉變。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 保佑著謝拉格子民的耶拉岡德，想必也希望為此做些什麼。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......恩希歐迪斯，恩希歐迪斯。要是沒有他，謝拉格也不至於......唉。", "name": "嚴肅的長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哎呀，畢竟大部分人，並不會對著雪山度過一生。", "name": "慈祥的長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我們啊，已經是老頭子了，就讓那些年輕人去過更舒服的生活，有什麼不好的呢？", "name": "慈祥的長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 只是，聖女大人，此行恐怕會很艱辛吧。", "name": "慈祥的長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 沒關係，有侍女照顧，加上希瓦艾什家的戰士會前來護送，沒什麼可擔憂我的。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#12$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 您也不用擔心談判桌上的麻煩......耶拉岡德一定會保佑祂的子民。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#12$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g7_thoroughfare", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 呼——這地方可真冷啊。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我好久沒到過呼口氣就能冒白煙的地方了。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 早知道這裡冷成這個鬼樣子，我就不該為了看一眼雪而申請來謝拉格出外勤。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哎，還好只是來接個人，而且人事幹員說了，要是下午四點還沒等到，就不用等了。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 應聘入職也敢隨便爽約，真不知道是什麼人。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我看看檔案......“初雪”，名字真冷，這身衣服看起來真暖和。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 得了，我還是去商鋪裡問問有沒有發熱暖貼賣吧。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 老闆，你們這裡有發熱暖貼嗎？", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哎，來了來了——什麼暖貼？我聽不太懂啊。", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你是外面來的遊客吧，是不是想要一杯暖茶？", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 這裡挺冷的，對吧？有的遊客說這裡冷得要命，也有人說不算什麼。", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我去倒杯茶，你先隨便看看。", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哎，好......", "name": "羅德島幹員"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 呼，這裡真是什麼都有，還都是些沒見過的東西。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_012"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 100.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 來，先把茶喝了，我們這裡要過雪原，都靠這個撐著。", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哎，好，謝謝。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你是哪裡來的？", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 唔，羅德島......？", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 好像有點耳熟，不過這裡遊客來來往往的，具體說了些什麼我也記不住啦。", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " （這幅畫像上的人怎麼有點眼熟......）", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哎呀，外面竟然有那麼多地方，等賺夠錢了，我就出去看看。", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " （讓我掏出照片看看。）", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你是剛到謝拉格，還是已經逛過了？這裡的紀念品......", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不好意思，我想請問一下，掛在這裡的畫像，謝拉格人長成這樣的多嗎？", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哎呀，這是什麼話？這是我們的聖女大人啊，哪能有和聖女大人相似的？", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 咳，咳咳咳......", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 以往啊，聖女大人的畫像只有幾幅，都是掛在各家族的宅邸前面，領民們自己前去祈禱。", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 說實話，那時候畫像和聖女大人本人像不像，大家都不知道。我們這些普通人，一年到頭來也只有大典能見到聖女本人。", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 那也是在廣場上隔著人山人海，遠遠地望一眼。", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 能聽到聖女大人的鈴音，得到耶拉岡德賜福，我們就心滿意足啦。", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不過後來不一樣了，謝拉格來了遊客，恩希歐迪斯老爺聽說外面許多人對聖女大人好奇，就叫大家做了許多畫像、刺繡還有雕像。", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 當然啦，老爺要我們做的畫像肯定是準的，畢竟老爺是常常能見到聖女大人本人的。", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 而且啊，現在的聖女大人就是他的親妹妹，他能不熟悉嗎？", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哈，還有這種事情啊......", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 那要是，比如說，聖女大人離開了謝拉格，會發生什麼？", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 啊？那怎麼可能？聖女大人平時是不下聖山的。", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 要是她下了山，那可就是出大事了。", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哎，小夥子，我說耶拉岡德在守護謝拉格，你肯定不信，是不是？你們外面來的遊客都不信。", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 呃，也不是完全不信......", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你聽我說，我生意能做下去，還真就是靠聖女帶來了耶拉岡德的神跡。", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 去年我這店鋪剛開張，他們就打起來了。", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 他們？", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 嘿，還不是三大家族互相鬧不和。", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 他們不僅打起來了，而且最要命的是把鐵路給炸斷了，遊客進不來，貨也進不來。", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我好不容易存的一點本錢剛投進去，這生意就做不成了，你說我可怎麼活啊。", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 那時候我就天天祈禱，求耶拉岡德給我一條生路。", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 結果我的祈禱真應驗了。聖女下了山，耶拉岡德顯現了神跡，當場就讓所有人都不敢造次了。", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哎，耶拉岡德在上......", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 那，允許我再好奇一下，聖女大人本人是怎樣的人？她，呃，好相處嗎？", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哈哈，瞧你這問題問的。", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 聖女大人就是耶拉岡德的領受者，因此她一定也很寬容吧。", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 要不是因為知道耶拉岡德是寬容的神，我哪敢回答你這麼冒犯的問題呢？", "name": "老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哈哈，那我確實是冒犯了......", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 謝啦，老闆，我挑一件斗篷帶走吧。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......有聖女大人刺繡的就不必了，普通紋樣就好，普通的就好。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g8_nobleroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 與您的會面這麼愉快，我卻要說句掃興的話了，真不好意思。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 聖女每日默思的時間就要到了，這件事我是不能怠慢的。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_222"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不不，本來就是我打擾了，請您按照您的日程來就好。", "name": "卡西米爾代表"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_222"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 說實話，此次來謝拉格，我的確沒有做見到喀蘭聖女的準備......", "name": "卡西米爾代表"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_222"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 卡西米爾既然有意與謝拉格互相瞭解，我當然很願意出面。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我想，對於卡西米爾商業聯合會來說，能與謝拉格的喀蘭聖女達成溝通這件事本身，就是一種挑釁。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_222"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......您指的是？", "name": "卡西米爾代表"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_222"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 過不了多久，監正會也會試圖接觸謝拉格。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_222"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......您瞭解的很多。", "name": "卡西米爾代表"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_222"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 而且看起來，這樣的發展很合您心意。", "name": "卡西米爾代表"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_222"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 這只是謝拉格對外接觸過程中必然的一步。真要說的話，我只希望監正會的代表也像您一樣友好，真誠地為雙方共同獲利而努力。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_222"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 聖女大人過譽了。", "name": "卡西米爾代表"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_222"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 今後商業聯合會與謝拉格的往來，如果能夠得到聖女大人的支持，想必會一帆風順。", "name": "卡西米爾代表"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_222"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 願耶拉岡德祝福您。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_222"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 糟糕，已經快到下午四點了......", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#2$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 234, "pro