長老"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我們看聖女批註經文看了這麼幾年，也不是認不出她的字跡。", "name": "慈祥的長老"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 看來她早就在心裡盤算好了。", "name": "慈祥的長老"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 成何體統，成何體統......！", "name": "嚴肅的長老"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 要是讓人知道聖女不僅下了山，還一去半個月，蔓珠院威嚴何在？聖女威嚴何在？", "name": "嚴肅的長老"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 耶拉岡德恐怕要降怒於我們了。", "name": "嚴肅的長老"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 唉，聖女才是領受耶拉岡德旨意的人，她說耶拉岡德容許了，那我們也只有相信。", "name": "慈祥的長老"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 這半個月，我們也只能對外宣稱，聖女大人在閉門靜修，暫不見人。", "name": "慈祥的長老"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 但恩雅這孩子啊，一直有自己的想法。她要下山做些什麼，一定也有她自己的道理。", "name": "慈祥的長老"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你看，過去這段時間，我們哪一次不是被她說得心服口服？", "name": "慈祥的長老"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......", "name": "嚴肅的長老"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 唉，罷了，如何應付來訪者，我也大致想好了。", "name": "嚴肅的長老"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g11_snowylane", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 從做燉菜的小餐館往裡走到第二個小巷口，是這裡吧......", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 再過五分鐘就四點了，怎麼還沒見到人影。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 照片再拿出來看看......不過喀蘭聖女，哪裡會認錯啊。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哎，這種沒人的小巷，會不會是站著被約進去，躺著被抬出來......", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 別回頭。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哇，我投降，我只是個遊客，也沒什麼錢，跟家裡也沒聯繫了，你殺我沒好處的......", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 噓，安靜。你是誰？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 呃，我說了我只是遊客......", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 公司？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 羅德島，一家醫藥企業，主要是治療礦石病的，可能在你們這裡沒什麼市場......", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 可別順手把刀抽出來啊。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 刺殺聖女，這罪名你可擔不起。", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 咳咳......實在抱歉，喀蘭的聖女大人！耶拉岡德在上，請不要對我動怒！", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#12$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 無妨，我是依照協議來幫助羅德島的。", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#12$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 而且，你連謝拉格人掛在嘴邊的頌詞都學會了？", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#4$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 呼，我可被你嚇壞了，這不就隨便想了一句我記住的頌詞。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......差一點就真動手了，那可就更嚇人了。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哎，可是你看，連你都知道我是聖女了，謝拉格肯定人人都知道，對吧？", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 要是這個用黑色衣服裹得嚴嚴實實的不是羅德島的人，而是別的什麼怪人，我又被他看見了的話。", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#10$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 聖女一個人跑出來的事情不就要傳開了嗎？", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#12$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 所以我只好從背後靠近，先把你的身份問清楚啦。", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#12$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#12$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我聽說的聖女大人可不是這樣的......", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 嗯？但是我是初雪，又不是聖女，不一樣也很正常吧？", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#4$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 要是你在羅德島上叫我聖女，我可是會把你的嘴凍住的哦。", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#4$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哈哈，好......", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 剛好四點鐘，你要是再晚來一點，恐怕我就離開了。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 唔，畢竟有很多人攔著我嘛，我也不知道自己能不能順利去羅德島。", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 對了，我聽說聖女不能隨意下山。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 嗯，但是外交代表求見，這就沒辦法了吧？", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#10$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 所以，我拜託雅兒去羅德島的時候，先繞路去見一見在謝拉格訪問的卡西米爾商業代表。", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 托她之口，我傳達了我的想法。", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 所以呢，過了幾天，對方求見聖女的消息就報到蔓珠院來了。", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你讓對方配合你下山？", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 當然不只是為了下山玩啦。", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#2$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 如果沒有這樣的契機，外來人不會知道謝拉格除了喀蘭貿易還有一位喀蘭聖女，更想不到聖女很樂意會見他們。", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#10$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 呵，如果一直都是恩希歐迪斯說了算，謝拉格恐怕......", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#10$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我聽說恩希歐迪斯是你的——", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ——說起來，我還從沒離開過謝拉格呢。", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#4$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " （咳，看來我剛剛多嘴了。）", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 嗯，我在登上羅德島之前也從沒離開過維多利亞。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 還好羅德島的廚子們來自泰拉各地，你不會餓著的。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不過想家還是難免的，家鄉菜和自家的菜終究不一樣。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 那，你後來回過家嗎？", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#5$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 怎麼突然問這個......", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我是感染者，家鄉不歡迎我，就算想回也回不去啦。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 啊，抱歉。", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我只是有點好奇，因為我以前只見過從外面回來的人。", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 有的人離開謝拉格，在外面生活了幾年，等他回來的時候，我就完全認不出他了。", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哎，可能是年輕人，一眨眼就長變樣了吧？", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 是哦，不過他不僅長高了，肩膀變得寬闊了......想法也和以前完全不一樣了。", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 以前離開謝拉格的人是少數，所以我一直在想，謝拉格外面到底是什麼樣子，他到底看到了什麼。", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 是不是每個人出去走一趟都會變得很不一樣。", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 走吧走吧，我已經等不及要去羅德島見雅兒了。", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#4$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哎，好。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 對了，剛剛聽說你是聖女的時候，我順便買了件斗篷。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 戴上兜帽，可以遮住你的臉，免得被人一眼認出來。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 咦，你想得很周到嘛。", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#4$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 幫我拿一下手上的書好嗎？我把斗篷披上。", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#4$1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 好——《四皇會戰簡史》？", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 啊，這本書是博士借給我的。", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#5$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我的房間裡還堆著好幾本博士借我的閒書呢，這一本打算在路上看完還回去，剩下的就下次再說吧。", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 說起來，我應該算是從沒見過博士吧......希望那個人不會催促我工作，畢竟我可是去羅德島度假的。", "name": "初雪"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 羅德島不是給幹員上班的地方嗎......", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 咳，但是祝你度假愉快。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}